<SEQUENCE TIMEOUT="" EXIT-ON="FAILURE">
  <COMMENT> exists - checks if a single file exists or not on an FTP server - returns true/false/unknown </COMMENT>
</SEQUENCE>

<SEQUENCE TIMEOUT="" EXIT-ON="FAILURE">
  <COMMENT>    note that this mechanism is WAY faster than doing an ls on the filename, expecially for very long directories </COMMENT>
</SEQUENCE>

<SEQUENCE TIMEOUT="" EXIT-ON="FAILURE">
